summary: AirMSPI_ORACLES_Terrain-projected_Georegistered_Radiance_Data are AirMSPI Terrain-projected georegistered radiance product acquired during the NASA ObseRvations of Aerosols above CLouds and their intEractionS (ORACLES) flight campaign Jul-Oct 2016. The ORACLES campaign occurred from Jul 28, 2016 to Oct 6, 2016 and the NASA ER-2 was based out of the Walvis Bay International Airport, Namibia.
